```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_returns.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        item_id,
        return_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY
                CASE WHEN status = 'approved' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ASC,
                return_date DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    item_id,
    return_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
    AND status = 'approved'
```

-- models/marts/fct_return_rates_by_category.sql
WITH items AS (
    SELECT
        oi.item_id,
        oi.product_id,
        oi.quantity,
        p.category_id
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
        ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
)
SELECT
    COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)') AS category_name,
    SUM(i.quantity) AS total_items_sold,
    SUM(COALESCE(r.quantity_returned, 0)) AS total_items_returned,
    CASE
        WHEN SUM(i.quantity) = 0 THEN 0
        ELSE SUM(COALESCE(r.quantity_returned, 0)) * 1.0 / SUM(i.quantity)
    END AS return_rate
FROM items i
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
    ON c.category_id = i.category_id
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} r
    ON r.item_id = i.item_id
GROUP BY
    COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)')
